{
  "message": "test(fuzz): fuzz_series_add corpus with 17 new seeds\n\nAdd structured corpus seeds covering:\n- Single element series (same/different indices)\n- Null + int, NaN + int operations\n- Int + float type coercion\n- Float + infinity/neg-infinity/NaN\n- Multiple overlapping indices with nulls\n- All-null and all-NaN series\n- Mixed scalar types on both sides\n- Negative int values, zero/neg-zero\n- Large + small series (12 vs 2 elements)\n- String index labels\n- Duplicate labels in same series\n\nAdded replay test to verify all seeds pass invariants.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
